longBusinessSummary: China New Town Development Company Limited engages in planning and developing new towns in the People's Republic of China. It operates through four segments: Land Development, Urbanization Development, Property Leasing, and Others. The company provides land infrastructure development services; constructs ancillary public facilities; and invests in new town projects. It also offers property leasing and management, real estate and enterprise investment consultation, management consulting, asset management, investment and asset development, and investment management services. The company was founded in 2002 and is based in Wan chai, Hong Kong.
